lookup — breaks immediately. You ask a
question. You get an answer. You run it

4
00:00:45,420 --> 00:01:04,600
What it actually does: next-token
prediction. At every step it estimates the
most likely continuation of everything

5
00:01:04,650 --> 00:01:22,700
Temperature zero makes the most probable
token always win. But probable is
conditioned on everything in the context.

6
